	   (40, 16, 'Wigglytuff', 'https://www.serebii.net/pokearth/sprites/frlg/40.png', 'It has a very fine fur. Take care not to make it angry, or it may inflate steadily and hit with a body slam.', 1, 1, '1', '2', 'Kanto'),
